Package dk.via.sep.server.networking.eventServerHandler

Interface EventServer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventServerCallback, java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventServerHandler
    public interface EventServer
extends EventServerCallback, java.rmi.Remote
    Event server interface that can be used for methods the client should not access. Currently empty as there is no need for any. If you wish to add remote methods, do so in the EventServerCallback interface.
